{"article_id":"AQj55LKZH36sivZU","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Obama ' s campaign said Wednesday","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"that Mitt Romney either lied to voters or to federal regulators about how long he ran his company ,","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"while the GOP candidate ' s team said","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"the \" felony \" accusation was so over-the-top","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"that the president should apologize for his aides ' behavior ;","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"voters were left to sort it all out .","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"The dust-up over Mr. Romney ' s time at private equity firm Bain Capital underscored the growing realization","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"that his business ties will come under scrutiny for the rest of the campaign","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"- a theme","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"the former Massachusetts governor ' s rivals started in the Republican primary .","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"Wednesday ' s charges stemmed from a report in the Boston Globe","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"that said","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"documents","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"filed with the Securities and Exchange Commission","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"show","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"Mr. Romney may have led Bain until 2002 , three years longer","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"than he claims .","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"The charge is significant","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"because the Obama campaign says","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"that Mr. Romney shares responsibility for the investments","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"Bain made between 1999 and 2002 ,","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"which led to jobs","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"being shipped off to China and India .","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"\" Either Mitt Romney , through his own words and his own signature , was misrepresenting his position at Bain to the SEC ,","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"which is a felony ,","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"or he was misrepresenting his position at Bain to the American people","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"to avoid responsibility for some of the consequences of his investments , \"","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"Stephanie Cutter , deputy campaign manager for the Obama campaign , told reporters in a conference call .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"\" If that ' s the case ,","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"if he was lying to the American people ,","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"then that is a real character and trust issue","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"that the American people need to take very seriously , \"","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"she said .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"The Romney camp said","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"the Globe report was \" not accurate , \"","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"and touted the findings of independent fact checkers","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"that agreed with them .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"Mr. Romney ' s aides also pointed to a story Wednesday by Fortune","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"that said","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"internal Bain documents showed","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"Mr. Romney had stopped managing the firm ' s clients","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"when he went to oversee the Salt Lake City Olympics .","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"In a statement to reporters , Romney campaign manager Matt Rhoades called the Obama team ' s accusations \" reckless and unsubstantiated . \"","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"\" President Obama ought to apologize for the out-of-control behavior of his staff ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"which demeans the office","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"he holds , \"","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"Bain Capital also released a statement","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"that supported Mr. Romney ' s claim","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"that he left in 1999","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"and that he had \" no involvement with the management or investment activities of the firm or with any of its portfolio companies since the day of his departure . \"","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"Democrats have demanded Mr. Romney release more tax returns","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"in order to give voters a better look at his finances ,","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"and said Thursday","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"that his role at Bain is critical","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"for voters to have a full picture","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"of how he approaches job creation .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"David Yepsen , director of the Paul Simon Public Policy Institute at Southern Illinois , said","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"Mr. Romney ' s successful business history will continue to dog him .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"\" There ' s no doubt","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"his complex finances makes this a hard story for Romney to control , \"","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"Mr. Yepsen said .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"the Romney camp deserves blame","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"for not having better answers ready .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"\" After running for president for years ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"he and his people should have known","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"this was coming","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"and disclosed a lot more a lot earlier","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"so that this was all an old story by now , \"","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"Mr. Yepsen said .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"Even before the Globe story took root ,","depth":3},{"id":72,"text":"the name-calling had begun early in the day","depth":3},{"id":73,"text":"when the Romney camp released a new ad , \" No Evidence , \"","depth":5},{"id":74,"text":"that said","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"Mr. Obama was lying to voters in his claim","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"that Mr. Romney had a hand in offshoring jobs .","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"\" When a president doesn ' t tell the truth .","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"How Can We Trust Him To Lead ? \"","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"Mr. Romney ' s ad retorts .","depth":5},{"id":80,"text":"The ad also highlighted the analysis of Factcheck.org ,","depth":5},{"id":81,"text":"which found","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"there was \" no evidence \"","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"that Mr. Romney shipped jobs overseas ,","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"as well as The Washington Post ,","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"which had reported the story","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"the Obama campaign cited","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"but whose fact-checker called the charge \" misleading . \"","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"The Globe report ,","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"she said ,","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"proved","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"that Mr. Romney was in \" full control of Bain Capital through 2002 \" and directly responsible for the related outsourcing , bankrupting and layoffs .","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"\" Whatever the consequences of Bain investments were ,","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"he was responsible , \"","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"she said .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":189,"left":165,"right":188,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":165,"left":100,"right":164,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":96,"right":99,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":96,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":99,"left":98,"right":5,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":2,"right":97,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":97,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":164,"left":103,"right":163,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":101,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":143,"right":162,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":1